![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c75f889d-25f9-4e63-853b-4178114e9b9e/260.jpg)

Rumors are running amok regarding the next Avenger's film, Avengers: Kang Dynasty and we are down to speculate (with a grain of salt of course. Speaking of course, DC is staying the course with the release of The Flash whether we like it or not! We cover all that and a do full recap and review of Batman & Superman: Battle of The Supersons in this jam-packed edition of the Major Issue Podcast!  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
